46h-13.8H199v13.8v13.8H212.8z M212.8,68.1h-8.3v-8.3v-8.3h8.3h8.3v8.3v8.3H212.8z M262.5,79.2h-2.8v-2.8 v-2.8h2.8h2.8v2.8v2.8H262.5z M290.1,79.2h-19.3V59.8V40.5h19.3h19.3v19.3v19.3H290.1z M290.1,73.7h13.8V59.8V46h-13.8h-13.8v13.8 v13.8H290.1z M290.1,68.1h-8.3v-8.3v-8.3h8.3h8.3v8.3v8.3H290.1z M245.9,68.1h-8.3v-8.3v-8.3h2.8h2.8v-2.8V46h-2.8h-2.8v-2.8v-2.8 h5.5h5.5V46v5.5h2.8h2.8v2.8v2.8h2.8h2.8v-8.3v-8.3h2.8h2.8v8.3v8.3h-2.8h-2.8v2.8v2.8H257h-2.8v2.8v2.8L245.9,68.1L245.9,68.1z M248.7,62.6h5.5v-2.8v-2.8h-2.8h-2.8v-2.8v-2.8h-2.8h-2.8v5.5v5.5H248.7z\"\/> <\/svg> <\/span> <\/td> <td> <div class=\"blue code_value\">\\ Cat Apple Mango Tomato \/<\/div> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr class=\"code_value\"> <td> 123456 <\/td> <td> 1A2B3C4D <\/td> <td> 9801234567 <\/td> <\/tr> <\/tbody> <\/table> <\/div> <h2>What does it do?<\/h2> <p> Converts data like Numbers, Email addresses or URLs and even small digital files into a bunch of words. <\/p> <div class=\"center\"> <img src=\"\/resource\/screen_guide.png\" alt=\"Captioned screenshot of the Windows GUI application\"\/> <\/div> <h2>How is it useful?<\/h2> <p> When asked for your telephone no. wouldn't it be nice if you had to say only four words instead of the usual ten. For example:<br> \"<strong><em>Cat Apple Mango Tomato<\/em><\/strong>\" against \"<strong><em>Nine Eight Zero One Two Three Four Five Six Seven<\/em><\/strong>\".<br><br> Also the chances of making mistakes are reduced since only carefully handpicked words that are simple and unambiguous and have distinct pronunciation are used.<br><br> Additionally check-summed WCode can be used to ensure correct delivery. <\/p> <h2>Where can it be used?<\/h2> <p>Where ever a human being is in-between a short digital communication across two non-connected computer systems. For example:<br> You need to tell your friend your bank account number. Even a single mistake can be disatrous. If you cannot SMS or email - and you must use traditional methods like writing or voice, WCode may be the best option.<\/p> <div class=\"center\"> <img src=\"\/resource\/general-use_case.png\" alt=\"WCodes are to be used in-between two disconnected computer systems\"\/> <\/div> <\/div> <div class='center' id='content-body-separator'><\/div> <div id='nav-list' class='center page-list'> <a id='nav-menu-prev' class='XURL item_block_container' href='\/patents' data-target='patents' data-title='Patents'> <img class='item_block_image item_block_image_visible' src='\/resource\/placeholder.svg' alt='Navigation - previous page tile'><div class='item_block_text'><div class='arrow'>&#x25C4;<\/div><div>Patents<\/div><\/div> <\/a><a id='nav-menu-next' class='XURL item_block_container' href='\/presentation' data-target='presentation' data-title='Presentation'> <img class='item_block_image item_block_image_visible' src='\/resource\/placeholder.svg' alt='Navigation - next page tile'><div class='item_block_text'><div>Presentation<\/div><div class='arrow'>&#x25BA;<\/div><\/div> <\/a><a id='nav-menu-up' class='XURL item_block_container center-arrow' href='\/' data-target='root' data-title='WCode'> <img class='item_block_image item_block_image_hidden' src='\/root.svg ' alt='Navigation - up level tile'><div class='item_block_text'><div><\/div><div class='arrow'>&#x25B2;<\/div><\/div> <\/a> <\/div>"}